00:43:36,720 --> 00:43:41,440
could just ship over and over and over and 
that keep that cycle time down. And there's  

473
00:43:41,440 --> 00:43:44,880
almost like implicit advice here is if 
you're working at a company that takes  

474
00:43:44,880 --> 00:43:49,680
a long time to ship, this is probably not 
a good place to be starting your career.

