00:44:16,400 --> 00:44:21,680
constant will hold even as AI starts to change 
the way that we build product and build teams?

482
00:44:21,680 --> 00:44:29,040
I think there are many things AI is changing and 
AI will change even if ... What did I work on  

483
00:44:29,040 --> 00:44:35,280
24 years ago or how did I do product management 
24 years ago is different than product management  

484
00:44:35,280 --> 00:44:40,400
today. The way we write PRDs, the way you 
do designs, the way you make decisions,  

485
00:44:40,400 --> 00:44:45,280
the fact that you have access to data today 
didn't really exist 24 years ago. The only  

