00:47:17,120 --> 00:47:20,080
Let's get you into trouble. Let's do it.

515
00:47:22,000 --> 00:47:29,200
I'll tell you, I actually know the answer to this 
question. What I hate about engineers is when you  

516
00:47:29,200 --> 00:47:35,440
on a project and they say, "Hey, I can't do 
anything because I do not have a PRD from a  

