00:47:49,600 --> 00:47:55,760
don't need to start with a PRD. They can have a 
whiteboarding session with a PM, with a designer,  

520
00:47:55,760 --> 00:48:01,040
they should have just an equal seat at the 
table in terms of what we are going to build  

521
00:48:01,040 --> 00:48:05,760
and then they co-create. They should co-create 
