00:48:27,360 --> 00:48:32,080
and is valid and I welcome that. I welcome 
their participation. I don't care about org  

527
00:48:32,080 --> 00:48:38,320
boundaries. Now, at the same, time, I will have 
an opinion about how we message our products.  

