00:48:42,720 --> 00:48:46,960
that I understand that or I will have 
an opinion about an ad campaign or how  

530
00:48:46,960 --> 00:48:53,200
we operationalize our product. So in 
that spirit, what I hate is if we are  

531
00:48:53,200 --> 00:48:58,720
blocked because a certain document was not 
written to the nth degree of specificity.

532
00:48:58,720 --> 00:49:02,400
I love that you answered the question. 
That's great. And I think what's also  

